{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/meets3to1","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/meets3to1"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"meets3to1","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"meets3to1","modules":[{"name":"Foundations"}],"externalID":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV9meets3to1Sbvp","role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If the computed contrast ratio between two given colors meets the 3:1 requirement"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"meets3to1","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"https://accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr":{"type":"link","title":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité"}],"url":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is for example the case for France with the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also named “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio"},"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"type":"link","title":"the following guidelines","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"the following guidelines"}],"url":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance"},"ic_layers.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","identi